➜收评：三大指数震荡走高创指涨1.26% 注册制次新股活跃
http://www.sohu.com/a/427621333_118392	25581
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201027/a36c6ca421ff40a8a05f25dcd7433838.png" width="100%" height="auto" /></p>
